<br>
Suffering is never a contribution. Try to remember that. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/bemarr.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=misty>Misty</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://users.bigpond.com/dwmac/eq12.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 235<br> <font color=#E9D756>(1/13/02 2:26:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=258.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: mushmouth strikes 2 - doh!</span><hr size=1> Kytherion:<br>
